ddf.catalog.plugin

Interface PostIngestPlugin

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CachingFederationStrategy, CatalogBackupPlugin, CatalogMetrics, EventProcessorImpl, FanoutEventProcessor, HistorianPlugin, IdentificationPlugin, RestReplicatorPlugin, SecurityLoggingPlugin

    public interface PostIngestPlugin
    Marker interface for services that wish to be called after any CreateResponse, UpdateResponse, or DeleteResponse is about to be returned to an endpoint.
    Author:
    michael.menousek@lmco.com

                throws PluginExecutionException
        Processes the CreateResponse.
        Parameters:
        input - the CreateResponse to process
        Returns:
        the value of the processed CreateResponse to pass to the next PostIngestPlugin, or if this is the last PostIngestPlugin to be called
